 ```
 
+Insert a deterministic review loop sidecar pair (`fix_rN` + `review_rN+1`):
+
+```bash
+waveplan-cli swim insert-fix-loop \
+  --schedule "$SCHEDULE" \
+  --review-schedule "$REVIEW_SCHEDULE" \
+  --task T1.1 \
+  --after-step S1_T1.1_review
+```
